metadata.name: abc of war
metadata.description:
Painted this on 24th February, the day when Russia began a full-scale invasion of Ukraine.

This wall was whitewashed within 60 hours. 

Immortalizing this by converting into a NFT. 

Painted this in Mumbai, India
